{"tid":2139060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金融時報：Biden當選會令中國有更大損失","createTime":"2020-08-04T04:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T00:24:37.000Z","uid":321519,"like":23,"dislike":292,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"6c03af2365653670d743309108d2ad27b79313c1","tid":2139060,"uid":321519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"雖然連登好多侵粉，但係FT話Biden當選會令中國有更大損失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//即使特朗普在十一月失敗，他也將成為具有里程碑意義的總統。他以一種現在看來不可逆轉的方式加強了美國對中國的立場。拜登的工作是說服選民，特朗普的功勞已經得到了體現。識別競爭對手需要耐心，甚至要有一定的偏執狂：也許沒有其他總統能做到。但是，同樣的特徵使他失去了耐心，並缺乏細微的建設和管理反中集團的工作資格。//（google translate)<br />\n所以連登仔咪迷戀Trump啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/30da66e4-9a73-11ea-adb1-529f96d8a00b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F30da66e4-9a73-11ea-adb1-529f96d8a00b&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd9Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=0c9a618b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/30da66e4-9a73-11ea-adb1-529f96d8a00b</a>"},{"pid":"9f9f03d09f668310df18590ab51a74be59c9a090","tid":2139060,"uid":137248,"like":24,"dislike":14,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"侵粉：FT奶共左媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bfcca2d92c1a4490dab8ae27d0885ddb20a872","tid":2139060,"uid":100155,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"克林頓在大選前表明對中國強硬，會就六四事件強烈懲罰中國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2108345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2108345</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"25c0b20fcf63d22501b1d4ba4457f2b070b7c591","tid":2139060,"uid":100155,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:56:56.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨參議員：中國正漸成長為一個值得尊敬的國家；反對向中國追究武漢肺炎責任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2133085\" data-auto-link